==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Irrelative
<hw>Ir*rel"a*tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not relative;
without mutual relations; unconnected.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Ir*rel"a*tive*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Irrelative chords</b></col> <fld>(Mus.)</fld>, <cd>those
having no common tone.</cd> -- <col><b>Irrelative repetition</b></col>
<fld>(Biol.)</fld>, <cd>the multiplication of parts that serve for a
common purpose, but have no mutual dependence or connection.</cd>
<au>Owen.</au></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Irrelavance</ent>⟦br⟧
